data.description: Pool Home. Private 1/2 Acre fenced yard in The Preserve, a pristine, gated community that allows personal truck. Relax on the 3,065 SQ FT screened Lanai w/ heated pool, wired Spa hot tub ,Summer kitchen. Huge private yard to rock in your hammock or tend the fenced garden. Neutral tile, Kit w/Granite, wood cabinets & large bar to Open concept Great Room. Dining area & flex living room. Owners suite w/walk in closet, soaking tub, step in shower, cabana door to pool. Split plan w/ ample bedrooms and guest bath. Laundry rm w/cabinets galore. ROOF 2020. AC 2019 GENERATOR, Water filter system.
